{"tid":1144300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸人既自私同香港人既自愛係唔同","createTime":"2019-05-08T04:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T04:38:01.000Z","uid":27793,"like":17,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"906e841a6fb5958a24fdee026f1af250fc0b14cd","tid":1144300,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"大陸人心口不一，明明唔鐘意都要充大頭笑住幫，事後又屌人又唔開心。<br />\n然後大陸人既自私係掠奪人地資源，仲要虛情假意話辛苦你喇唔好意思，但仍然要你付出。<br />\n<br />\n香港人心口通常一致，想西臉就西。但人地需要幫助既時候會突然幫一把。人地幫自己會婉拒或者唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n有感而發，因為遇到唔止一兩個大陸人係咁，成長環境真係好影響一個人品格價值觀。"},{"pid":"30608afffeaf3efdd51dee2e54068cc289dd6568","tid":1144300,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:17:44.000Z","msg":"香港人？？？？？"},{"pid":"862b153537413cc89048642d9dde992016fa7a65","tid":1144300,"uid":113373,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捍衛香港 終局之戰<br />\n反對修訂逃犯條例</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">星期六 早上8點半 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ba24b972450f3f6bc00e610f2532c15f9c8bdccf","tid":1144300,"uid":88723,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"香港人係至尊無上既種族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dd72c27a5f1f45dfc7473cdd37ced83b7f4025","tid":1144300,"uid":213877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"香港人分別不大"},{"pid":"4835dd7d90d777d1b24f25e929c0ec8479d7c8db","tid":1144300,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"聽人講過香港人有面惡心善特質"},{"pid":"897fe4e30a26c7bf4735a759f6bdddb5ab131519","tid":1144300,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39dd72c27a5f1f45dfc7473cdd37ced83b7f4025","tid":1144300,"uid":213877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"香港人分別不大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"初頭我都咁諗<br />\n但大陸人真係更加衰到難以形容<br />\n雖然香港人d西，投訴，怨言都搞到人抖唔到氣<br />\n但大陸人既心底既自私同賤簡直刷新我眼界<br />\n好似見到蛇識痾尿<br />\n定係我年紀細on9未見識過"},{"pid":"4810d24d9be4106763b23d7581f37924e8814000","tid":1144300,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b27c8315088d05afe46d7499efcf9ba673df18c","tid":1144300,"uid":216477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0adb84c729725c732eaef8553352b1fb3ad61aec","tid":1144300,"uid":27793,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4835dd7d90d777d1b24f25e929c0ec8479d7c8db","tid":1144300,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"聽人講過香港人有面惡心善特質"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"係啊係啊，就係咁既感覺。<br />\n之前成日西臉既同事成日拔刀相助"},{"pid":"851fadacbd176503010fe082b4de3d11ac5d973c","tid":1144300,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b27c8315088d05afe46d7499efcf9ba673df18c","tid":1144300,"uid":216477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"當然閪起上嚟係好mean好仆街"},{"pid":"865388d971d50e7b0a245f3f02ddc1638dab8a16","tid":1144300,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"